para_trans: Included in the cabinet of Ma. Minister / M.A. Regarding the distribution of the office hall to the Minister of State.
Government Decision No. Shakaja-1924 / Q. No. 120/2024 Niwas-19,

Government Decision: - Ma. Mr. Chhagan Chandrabhaga Chandrakant Bhujbal, Ma. For the office of the Minister, the second floor of the Mantralaya Extension Building is located in Hall No. 201, 202, 204, WR are being allocated.
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
